{"tid":1581290,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"良心食堂 - 紅伶飯店","createTime":"2019-09-19T13:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T12:36:42.000Z","uid":40662,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e77154f67821b53d5332e7a80d55f4e7f3242045","tid":1581290,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"完整介紹：<br />\n<a href=\"http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.com/2019/09/CoCoAndMe-Sep.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F09%2FCoCoAndMe-Sep.html%3Fm%3D1&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=ef1b177a\" target=\"_blank\">http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.com/2019/09/CoCoAndMe-Sep.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n以下文字係轉載自某群組：<span style=\"color: red;\">「你哋會生存落去㗎！」</span>朋友同老闆娘講。今日同老友又去咗呢間小店度打冷，坐喺我哋隔離有位藍士就喺度批評示威者近日嘅做法（聽佢口吻唔算好藍所以唔用藍屍稱呼），然後已經七十幾歲嘅老闆娘就即刻屌鳩佢話：<span style=\"color: red;\">「你知唔撚知大陸當年幾衰，我嗰時走落嚟係為咗乜？班後生仔係你哋帶大嘅，而家你亂咁打佢哋，佢哋冇阿爸阿媽㗎？一日未定罪你都唔可以咁！咁同以前有乜分別？」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下個招牌都話畀你聽佢哋有幾黃！呢度一向好多後生仔幫襯，老闆娘熱情豪邁真個性，啤酒夠凍吹水宵夜一流，大大話話幫襯咗四十幾次，老闆娘話早排生意差咗好多，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家嚟多啲，如果唔係好大機會喺過年後就會冇咗呢間全香港最好食嘅打冷！<br />\n<br />\n《紅伶飯店》<br />\n<br />\n地址：佐敦吳松街19號地下<br />\n電話：2385 3524<br />\n營業時間：星期一至日：18:00 - 04:00<br />\n<br />\n各項評分（ 冚唪唥十個㊣）<br />\n食物質素：食出同舟共濟嘅人情味！<br />\n抵食程度：良心無價！<br />\n服務態度：人話難求！<br />\n衛生：心靈潔淨冇雜質！<br />\n環境：自己入嚟感受一下！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O98LY7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO98LY7U.jpg&h=1e9f26f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3pPCQeA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3pPCQeA.jpg&h=ee39673f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oNvKveB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoNvKveB.jpg&h=70995c07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEraqNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEraqNX.jpg&h=d6ec22ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97c8WUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97c8WUD.jpg&h=298ba5e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrZy71i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrZy71i.jpg&h=87ff9ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HNpveF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HNpveF.jpg&h=3cc77ee9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfca9f9a74eb065687d37134c13253579fcc0d04","tid":1581290,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=28b2ef6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"ab108206f9f5d3a6625e9e16a98d8837cf25e91f","tid":1581290,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:23:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c